As for your second question this is possible. You can do a [GET statuses/user_timeline](https://dev.twitter.com/rest/reference/get/statuses/user_timeline) (or however you are looking for tweets). Any tweets you get that way (or any other way) with images will contain [entities](https://dev.twitter.com/overview/api/entities-in-twitter-objects#media) which you can use to get a link for the media. Simply use a regex or just search the tweet for the hashtag you want and then download the media from the entity.

